---
const pills = [
  "Empresas em expansão",
  "Equipe comercial ativa",
  "Necessidade de leads qualificados",
  "Presença digital subutilizada",
  "Busca por previsibilidade",
];
---

<section class="section proof-section" id="proof-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="proof-card">

      <div class="proof-header">
        <p class="section-label proof-label" id="proof-label" data-state="checking" aria-label="Para quem faz sentido">
          <span class="pf-checking" aria-hidden="true">verificando perfil<span class="pf-dots"><span>.</span><span>.</span><span>.</span></span></span>
          <span class="pf-match" aria-hidden="true">para quem faz sentido</span>
        </p>
        <span class="pf-count">{pills.length} perfis</span>
      </div>

      <div class="proof-copy">
        <h2>Mais aderente para empresas com operação real, equipe e meta de crescimento.</h2>
        <p>
          Essa estrutura tende a gerar mais resultado quando a empresa já possui
          processo comercial, equipe ativa e necessidade de previsibilidade. Em
          especial para negócios com
          <strong>mais de 7 funcionários</strong> e atuação na
          <strong>Grande Goiânia</strong>, com foco estratégico em
          <strong>Aparecida de Goiânia</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="proof-divider">
        <span class="proof-divider-label">perfis compatíveis</span>
      </div>

      <ul class="pf-pills" id="pf-pills">
        {pills.map((text, i) => (
          <li class="pf-pill" style={`--i:${i}`}>
            <svg class="pf-check" width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
            {text}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
  (function () {
    const section = document.getElementById("proof-section");
    const label = document.getElementById("proof-label");
    const pills = document.getElementById("pf-pills");
    if (!section || !label || !pills) return;

    const items = pills.querySelectorAll(".pf-pill");
    let ran = false;

    function activate() {
      if (ran) return;
      ran = true;

      /* 1 — label: checking → match after short pause */
      setTimeout(() => {
        label.dataset.state = "match";
      }, 480);

      /* 2 — pills: staggered reveal */
      items.forEach((item, idx) => {
        setTimeout(() => {
          item.classList.add("is-visible");
        }, 300 + idx * 110);
      });
    }

    var observer = new IntersectionObserver(
      function (entries) {
        if (entries[0].isIntersecting) {
          activate();
          observer.disconnect();
        }
      },
      { threshold: 0.2 }
    );
    observer.observe(section);
  })();
</script>

<style>
  /* ── Card unificado ── */
  .proof-card {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.01) 100%),
      rgba(6, 10, 18, 0.9);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(1.18);
    box-shadow:
      0 24px 56px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28),
      inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02),
      0 0 48px rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.04);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .proof-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.15rem 0.8rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.06);
  }

  .pf-count {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.45);
    font-family: monospace;
  }

  /* ── Copy ── */
  .proof-copy {
    padding: 1.1rem 1.15rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.05);
  }

  .proof-copy h2 { margin-bottom: 0.55rem; }

  .proof-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-3);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.64;
  }

  .proof-copy strong { color: var(--text-2); font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── Divider row ── */
  .proof-divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.15rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.05);
  }

  .proof-divider::before,
  .proof-divider::after {
    content: "";
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.18), transparent);
  }

  .proof-divider-label {
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.35);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── Badges aqua glassmorphism ── */
  .pf-pills {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.15rem;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pf-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.42rem;
    padding: 0.42rem 0.85rem 0.42rem 0.68rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.18);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(1.3);
    box-shadow:
      0 2px 12px rgba(255, 31, 143, 0.08),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    color: #ff8fce;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.88);
    transition:
      opacity 320ms var(--ease-out),
      transform 380ms var(--spring);
  }

  .pf-pill.is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1);
  }

  .pf-pill:active { transform: scale(0.95); opacity: 0.8; }

  .pf-check {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    color: #ff60b5;
  }

  /* ── Label states ── */
  .proof-label[data-state="checking"]::before {
    animation: proof-dot-pulse 0.65s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes proof-dot-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1;   box-shadow: 0 0 7px currentColor; }
    50%       { opacity: 0.2; box-shadow: none; }
  }

  .pf-checking { display: inline; }
  .pf-match    { display: none; }

  .proof-label[data-state="match"] .pf-checking { display: none; }
  .proof-label[data-state="match"] .pf-match {
    display: inline;
    animation: pf-resolve 320ms var(--spring) forwards;
  }

  @keyframes pf-resolve {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
  }

  .pf-dots span {
    display: inline-block;
    animation: pf-blink 1.2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .pf-dots span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .pf-dots span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

  @keyframes pf-blink {
    0%, 80%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    40%            { opacity: 0.15; }
  }

  /* ── Mobile ── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .proof-header { padding: 0.72rem 0.9rem; }
    .proof-copy   { padding: 0.9rem 0.9rem 0.8rem; }
    .proof-divider { padding: 0.5rem 0.9rem; }
    .pf-pills     { padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem; gap: 0.42rem; }
    .pf-pill      { font-size: 0.76rem; padding: 0.38rem 0.75rem 0.38rem 0.6rem; }
  }
</style>
